      <title>Less Design, Better Writing</title>
      <link>https://minimalissimo.com/moods/less-design-better-writing</link>
      <guid>moods/less-design-better-writing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Aug 2020 00:00:00 +0200</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[<p>Writing by hand may be a forgotten art, but we should all own one beautifully designed pen, whether we write notes, stories, or even sketches. An ode to the simple pen (and pencil), the minimal pen, and the love of writing.</p><img alt="" src="https://minimalissimo.com/content/moods/66_less-design-better-writing/ajoto-pen-2.jpg"><img alt="" src="https://minimalissimo.com/content/moods/66_less-design-better-writing/ajoto-pen-3.jpg"><img alt="" src="https://minimalissimo.com/content/moods/66_less-design-better-writing/ajoto-pen.jpg"><img alt="" src="https://minimalissimo.com/content/moods/66_less-design-better-writing/ito-bindery-drawing-pad-black-angle_d356860a-3091-456f-a34f-10d70b1a61b7_1800x1800.jpg"><img alt="" src="https://minimalissimo.com/content/moods/66_less-design-better-writing/pen-type-a.jpg"><img alt="" src="https://minimalissimo.com/content/moods/66_less-design-better-writing/pen-type-b-black_1800x1800.jpg"><img alt="" src="https://minimalissimo.com/content/moods/66_less-design-better-writing/pen-type-b-with-sleeve-polished_1800x1800.jpg"><img alt="" src="https://minimalissimo.com/content/moods/66_less-design-better-writing/travelpen_closeup_lidoff_ma_web_v6__78581.1495040923.jpg"><img alt="" src="https://minimalissimo.com/content/moods/66_less-design-better-writing/travelpen_horizontal_pa_web__15346.1495637584.jpg"><img alt="" src="https://minimalissimo.com/content/moods/66_less-design-better-writing/worther-shorty-ballpoint-white-and-black-with-mark_1800x1800.jpg">]]></description>
