        <item>
      <title>MASS Series &#8220;SUMI LIMITED&#8221;</title>
      <link>https://minimalissimo.com/articles/mass-series-sumi-limited</link>
      <guid>articles/mass-series-sumi-limited</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Aug 2020 00:00:00 +0200</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="MASS Series SUMI LIMITED by FIL" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-6.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-6.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-6.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-6.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-6.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-6.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-6.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-6.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<p>When there is a story behind a design or something unusual that inspires a design, it makes for a more compelling project, rather than design for the sake of design. So when we recently spoke to Kumamoto interior and lifestyle brand, FIL, they introduced a furniture line inspired by the “inky black” landscape of Noyaki; Aso’s annual controlled burning of the grassland. Noyaki is a millennium old tradition in Aso to preserve the grasslands. The landscape is a symbol of the human relationship with nature. Locals have been and continue to maintain and use the grasslands to undertake sustainable farming and agriculture.</p>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="MASS Series SUMI LIMITED by FIL" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-2.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-2.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-2.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-2.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-2.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-2.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-2.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-2.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="MASS Series SUMI LIMITED by FIL" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-3.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-3.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-3.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-3.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-3.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-3.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-3.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-3.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="MASS Series SUMI LIMITED by FIL" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-1.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-1.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-1.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-1.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-1.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-1.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-1.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-1.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<p>The <a href="https://sumi.fillinglife.co/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">MASS Series &ldquo;SUMI LIMITED&rdquo;</a> features a contrast between different materials, combining a steel frame with charred cedar, which beautifully represents the inky black landscape. This series was conceived with a view to gaining a deeper understanding of Noyaki, a tradition serving as one of the mainstays of Aso’s scenery. This tradition has preserved Aso’s majestic scenery for over a thousand years, forging deep bonds amongst locals. In the history behind this landscape, created by people and nature over the centuries, one can find a hint to a rich and fulfilling life.</p>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="MASS Series SUMI LIMITED by FIL" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-5.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-5.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-5.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-5.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-5.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-5.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-5.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-5.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="MASS Series SUMI LIMITED by FIL" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-7.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-7.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-7.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-7.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-7.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-7.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-7.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-7.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="MASS Series SUMI LIMITED by FIL" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-4.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-4.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-4.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-4.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-4.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-4.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-4.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-4.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<p>“SUMI LIMITED” is designed to express the unique Aso experience, where people and nature co-exist and thrive together in a majestic yet harsh volcanic environment, along with the seeds of life sprouting from the inky black world of Noyaki. This series is limited to just 25 units sold annually. The number is based on the 25 Oguni cedar saplings which were granted in the Edo period to grow forests.</p>
<p>Looking further into the design of the furniture line, cedar is charred to gain glossiness and organic features with defined grains. Charred colour acts as a reminder of Noyaki. It represents Aso’s history and beauty of a harmonic lifestyle with nature. The series includes a lounge chair, dining chair, coffee table, two stools, and a coat hanger. The clean-cut design with smoothly planed cedar and elegantly prepared steel frames invites you to touch and feel it.</p>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="MASS Series SUMI LIMITED by FIL" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-8.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-8.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-8.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-8.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-8.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-8.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-8.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-8.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="MASS Series SUMI LIMITED by FIL" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-9.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-9.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-9.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-9.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-9.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-9.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-9.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/187_mass-series-sumi-limited/sumi-limited-9.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<p>FIL is based in Minami-Oguni, Kumamoto prefecture. Rather than just making products, FIL came about with an ambition to protect and preserve the landscape and natural resources that communities cherished and harness it for future generations. FIL makes locally produced furniture, aroma products, and other daily-use items, pursuing the values of “fulfilling life” through design.</p>]]></description>
    </item>
        <item>
      <title>Casa Em Campolide</title>
      <link>https://minimalissimo.com/articles/casa-em-campolide</link>
      <guid>articles/casa-em-campolide</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jul 2020 00:00:00 +0200</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="Casa Em Campolide by Aires Mateus" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-6.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-6.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-6.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-6.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-6.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-6.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-6.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-6.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<p><a href="https://www.airesmateus.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Aires Mateus</a> has done it again with another stunning minimalist dwelling to capture our hearts and imagination. Led by brothers Manuel and Francisco, the studio has designed the gorgeous <a href="https://www.dslstudio.it/place/aires-mateus-arquitectos-casa-em-campolide/#2" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Casa Em Campolide</a>, located in Lisbon, Portugal, that pairs modern architectural form with a unique blend of materials for a captivating dwelling that has us looking twice.</p>
<p>The structure of Casa Em Campolide is articulated as a simple white box with a central courtyard. The traditional style of this home is seen often in warm climate areas of Europe: the white facade reflects sunlight and the courtyard encourages air flow, keeping the home cool while maintaining minimal energy output. It is clever of Aires Mateus to keep this architectural form in their contemporary design: it is a style that works with the surrounding dwellings and nods to historical architecture.</p>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="Casa Em Campolide by Aires Mateus" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-12.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-12.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-12.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-12.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-12.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-12.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-12.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-12.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="Casa Em Campolide by Aires Mateus" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-7.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-7.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-7.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-7.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-7.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-7.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-7.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-7.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<p>Where this home differs from tradition, however, is first observed in the window openings. Each window varies slightly in size and location—a very unusual design choice for most homes. But as we have come to expect from Aires Mateus’ work, the choice is not without reason. Casa Em Campolide’s window size and placement are correlated to the needs of the interior. Truly a case of form follows function! Oversized windows in the courtyard bring light and nature pouring into the interior, while smaller windows give just enough light and view to the stairwell and more private interior spaces. Aires Mateus’ utilisation of the clean white facade is the perfect canvas for this unique arrangement of windows: rather than looking awkward, the assortment of windows adds decor and interest to every side of the exterior.</p>
<p>Framed in a soft, light wood, the window trim gives the viewer of Casa Em Campolide a hint of what is to come on the inside. Wood is the main material in use here, an interesting choice given its contrast to the clean white facade. Aires Mateus have certainly taken a generous approach when it comes to the use of wood on the finishes: they use it as the flooring, ceiling, and wall panelling.</p>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="Casa Em Campolide by Aires Mateus" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-11.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-11.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-11.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-11.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-11.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-11.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-11.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-11.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="portrait" style="padding-bottom: 150%"><img alt="Casa Em Campolide by Aires Mateus" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 336px , 468px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-8.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-8.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-8.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-8.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-8.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-8.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-8.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-8.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<p>Upon entering the living room, one could easily be overwhelmed by the sheer quantity of the wood materials. But once one’s eyes settle on the space we see the details that are so crucial to pulling off this design move. Beams along the ceiling run in the opposite direction of the wood underlayment, creating structural depth. The window frames are slightly inset, giving the same effect as the ceiling beams. All of the accents in the interior are black and therefore stand out dramatically against the lighter tone of the wood. Black metal makes up the kitchen backsplash and worktop, and hangs above the table in the form of pendant lights. It is used again as the primary colour in the furnishings: the dining chairs and living room set vary in material but not in colour. </p>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="Casa Em Campolide by Aires Mateus" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-1.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-1.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-1.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-1.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-1.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-1.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-1.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-1.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="Casa Em Campolide by Aires Mateus" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-10.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-10.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-10.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-10.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-10.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-10.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-10.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-10.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<p>The bathroom of Casa Em Campolide is covered in marble. The marble could be seen as clashing with the wood, but we prefer to think of it as another small stroke of genius by Aires Mateus. Marble, while opposite in materiality, brings together the two accent colours of the design—black and white. The marble bathroom stands out equally as much as the wood-clad living and bedrooms, but this time uniting the monochromatic details with the stone’s natural colour.  </p>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="portrait" style="padding-bottom: 150%"><img alt="Casa Em Campolide by Aires Mateus" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 336px , 468px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-2.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-2.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-2.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-2.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-2.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-2.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-2.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-2.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="Casa Em Campolide by Aires Mateus" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-9.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-9.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-9.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-9.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-9.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-9.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-9.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-9.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<p>Lastly, one cannot overlook the importance of the windows in this home. The windows are crucial to pulling off this unique design. Just when the wood interior feels overwhelming, one turns towards the oversized window in the room and is refreshed by the green of the courtyard. Similarly, the black accents never feel too dark because they are flooded by natural light from the oversized windows. Aires Mateus Architects are truly an exemplary designers, and Casa Em Campolide is a project that we will continue to study as an example of unique minimalist design.</p>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="landscape" style="padding-bottom: 66.666666666667%"><img alt="Casa Em Campolide by Aires Mateus" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 504px, 702px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-3.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-3.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-3.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-3.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-3.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-3.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-3.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-3.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>
<figure class="img-figure"><div class="img-wrapper" data-orientation="portrait" style="padding-bottom: 150%"><img alt="Casa Em Campolide by Aires Mateus" class="img" data-original="100w" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 446px) 402px, (max-width: 600px) 336px , 468px" src="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-5.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60" srcset="https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-5.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60 402w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-5.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60 504w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-5.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60 702w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-5.jpg?w=402&amp;h=402&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 804w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-5.jpg?w=504&amp;h=504&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1008w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-5.jpg?w=702&amp;h=702&amp;q=60&amp;dpr=2 1404w,https://minimalissimo.imgix.net/content/articles/186_casa-em-campolide/casa-em-campolide-aires-mateus-5.jpg?q=60"></div></figure>]]></description>
